Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个  那种机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办啊  约翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗  Exia的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要妨碍我们行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了根除战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯了吗  Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米海尔  迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚·厄德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  摧毁目标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia在和Throne战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才Virtue好像也加入了其中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连提耶利亚也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然Gundam之间相互厮杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好会两败俱伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好啊  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一体的做法让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个不错的男的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他们的行动也可能是计划的一部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们采取的这种行动或许也在计划之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯托拉托斯发来了紧急密码消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在待命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让他尽可能阻止战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  根据现场情况  以自己的判断为主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:03:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就等于是随便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有失战术预报员的脸面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷路亚你呢  要出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在这里保护普特利麦奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此  这里也并不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然心里很想出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会乱来啊  那个淘气包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂  没能阻止  没能阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗  你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  多亏如此  皇小姐也沉下气来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我也能理解刹那的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是想成为Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为实现根除纷争的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说  我很想干一场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击了  哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  洛克昂·斯托拉托斯  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  Exia向新型的Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  会如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红龙  对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这世界能改变就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是采取何种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之间的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预想得还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转到第三阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法挽回了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采用S32阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到还会和你搭档使用阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  Virtue  还在继续和Throne战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还采用了战术阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S32  D07  甚至还使用了F52
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚和刹那吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  对接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为  我会给你们留下这种时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以这种机动性的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  机体的输出功率…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,System down？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让与吠陀进行资料连接的机体全部被制抑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是Gundam Nadleeh的真正实力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅赐予了提耶利亚·厄德的Gundam Meister的试验系统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们并不适合当Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们罪该万死！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试验系统被强制解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7区域内的部分数据被窜改了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个数据区域到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然连我也无法访问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吠陀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Dynames吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就是三对三了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩组队战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就玩玩看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米海尔  妮娜  撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这样吧  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Gundam彼此之间争斗  那会妨碍计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  知道…啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我们来  你有更需要去战斗的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗  洛克昂·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  应该说是尼尔·迪兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔·迪兰地？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  居然看了我的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过吠陀拜读了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7的情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂  你成为Gundam Meister以来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要复仇的人之一  就在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁吉斯共和国反政府武装游击队KPSA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰·伊布拉希姆  乃是其成员之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索兰·伊布拉希姆  代号刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是刹那？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  他是杀害你父母和妹妹的组织中的成员之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的仇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7台Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经束手无策了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果胡乱出兵而拖垮军队的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我方阵营的经济就会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就只能接受他们的要求  解除武装了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这么做的话  那各国将会面临名誉扫地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声称是Celestial Being相关人员的人通过网络和我们接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织的相关资料也传了一些过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是内部分裂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来神还没有舍弃我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在受到攻击的爱丽丝公司工厂一带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量死者家属聚集在一起进行哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动攻击的三台MS被证实是新型Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此过激行为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝  花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  你回日本去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休学可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你能来陪我我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你不能一直待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我把你孤伶伶留在这里  这种事我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈你的梦想是去宇宙工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因为我而破坏你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使现在在一起  以后也会很难过的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直感到自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈会一直后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  能把我的梦想托付给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现梦想  这就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  去实现我的梦想吧  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方睡觉的话会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我介绍该由男孩子开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我叫沙慈·克洛斯罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝·哈莱维
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照了  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然直接叫名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  要你帮我做那么麻烦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是拉古那·哈贝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线性火车公司的总裁  国际经济集团的首席人物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不仅拥有建造MS的财力  也能自由地使用轨道电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  取材就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么啊  对方是我们的大股东哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去调查的话不会有好结果的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:16:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要秘密调查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会停的  好不容易才有点线索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是隶属KPSA的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自克鲁吉斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游击队的少年士兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂  三位一体说的那些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的双亲和妹妹是在KPSA的自杀炸弹式恐怖袭击中丧生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都起源于与太阳光发电计划一同出现的\N全世界范围的石油输出限制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么要停止使用化石燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  情况最恶劣的还是中东诸国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于输出限制  国家经济萧条  国民苦于贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穷困的人只能依靠神明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好听从神的代言人的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——那些只知道财富和权力的肤浅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  才引发了持续20多年的太阳光发电纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在神的土地上的人们的圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是些想当然的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然单方面提出输出限制的联合国也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是神或者宗教的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是太阳光发电系统也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  世界不可避免地就此扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被KPSA利用和继续并不希望的战斗也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我被卷进这种扭曲中  失去了家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  才接受成为Meister的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己很矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做的和恐怖袭击差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法阻绝不断的暴力  而选择了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也算是为了让那种悲剧不再发生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要让这个世界从根本上发生改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能拥有抑制世界的压倒性力量的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断杀人的惩罚  我会在世界改变后再去承受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在此之前有件事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  我极其想朝你开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我为家人报仇  报仇雪恨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚信不移
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说「所以我没有错」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界上没有神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么  索兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世界上没有神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不算答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信神并知道没有神的那个男人就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KPSA的领导者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…萨谢斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在莫拉利亚隶属于PMC
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民间军事公司？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:20:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游击队之后是佣兵吗  那不是战争狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在莫拉利亚的战场上  我和那家伙遇上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那个时候你从驾驶舱里出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了确认那家伙的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道那家伙的神到底在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…那家伙的心里没有神的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直以来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  我就问一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在用Exia做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我开枪的话就做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能替我去实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请替我改变这扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我活着的话就会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是作为索兰·伊布拉希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作为Celestial Being的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会坐上Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  傻得我都不想开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个无可救药的Gundam笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是最好的赞美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到啊  会被Gundam攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙突然发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还吻了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是遵照拉古那的指示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据情况可能还会再与Gundam战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划的巨大变化急剧地改变了世界的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中  人们就只能流泪  战斗和死去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「变革之刃」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.34,0:23:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种苦恼该向谁倾诉
